<h3 class="subtitle-about">  <i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i>  
  Our Founder</h3>

<p id="Liv_Founder">
Founder Information
Name: Dr. Evelyn Kaganda
Role: Founder and CEO
Background: Dr. Evelyn Kaganda is an esteemed educationist and visionary leader with over 15 years of experience in shaping academic and professional success. Holding a Doctorate in Educational Management, she has a profound passion for empowering students and professionals to achieve their highest potential through innovative learning methods.

Dr. Kaganda's vision stems from her belief that education is the cornerstone of societal transformation. Her dedication to creating accessible, quality education platforms led to the establishment of HigherCareer Academy, which aims to bridge the gap between academic excellence and career preparedness.</p>

<h3 class="subtitle-about"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i>School History</h3>

<p id="Liv_History">HigherCareer Academy was established in 2015 with a mission to redefine educational excellence by integrating advanced digital learning tools and a student-centered approach. Initially starting as a small institution in Tanzania, the academy focused on providing supplementary learning programs for primary and secondary school students.

As the demand for comprehensive, career-focused education grew, HigherCareer Academy expanded its services to include vocational training, professional certifications, and e-learning solutions. By 2020, the academy launched its online platform, enabling students across the globe to access tailored academic resources and interactive learning environments.

Today, HigherCareer Academy stands as a premier educational institution, renowned for its commitment to nurturing students' academic growth and preparing them for dynamic career paths. Through state-of-the-art facilities, experienced educators, and an inclusive approach, the academy continues to empower learners to excel in a competitive world.

Motto: "Transforming Education, Inspiring Success."</p>

<h3 class="subtitle-about"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
  Our Mission</h3>

<p id="Liv_Mission">
Quality education and discipline are our priority. We focus on shaping students into responsible and ethical individuals through a balanced approach of academics and values.</p>

